title: The Muppets and John Denver-A Christmas Together
description:
Source: 1998 CD 13 Song Release
-
The Muppets and John Denver-A Christmas Together 320cbr (Big Papi) 1998 
-
By Carl in Seattle
A year ago I reviewed a different edition of this CD which had three songs missing--"Have Yourself a Merry Little Christmas", "When the River Meets the Sea", and "Little Saint Nick". It is nice to see that the original complete 13-song version of the album is now available again. Our four children, now ages 14 to 34, all grew up listening to this recording. We own probably 50 Christmas CDs, ranging from classical to jazz to pop. If I could own only one Christmas CD, it would be this one. Exquisitely arranged and recorded, it is a true holiday classic.
